text: Metodija Bešliovski (born August 19, 1996) is a Macedonian professional basketball Small forward who currently plays for Kožuv in the Macedonian First League. ==References== ==External links== * at Eurobasket.com * at Balkanleague.net Category:1996 births Category:Sportspeople from Skopje Category:Macedonian men's basketball players Category:Living people Category:Small forwards
